<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Yes, the gem you get from Bubar *IS* called the sparkling Sapphire! If you identify it, it is the Gem of Righteousness. The reason it's called that is because you're supposed to trick Toxidil with a gem from Norressa that he thinks is what's in the box! You got the right gem, don't worry. Maybe check a little more into your quests too, it'll save you a lot of hastle.</font></td></tr></table>
